::Cygnar::
       He nods happy with the results of his inquiries and sends out replies 
to both.

To Tyrael:
       "Yes, we shall meet then at the small island to the northeast of the 
Northern continent on this world.  I must ask that you come alone.  As will 
I, and our ... other guest.  Cygnar out."

To Rodimus:
       "I am glad to have your support Rodimus Prime.  There will be a 
meeting at these coordinates, (Transmitting the coordinates of the small 
island to the northeast of the Northern continent) in one day's time.  I 
would be most pleased if you would meet me there, along with our other ally."

--part1_fd.1f0c65c5.2ad24b0c_boundary
